        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Block All New Oil Exports Act or the BAN Oil Exports Act</b></p> <p>This bill amends the Energy Policy and Conservation Act to require the President to ban the exportation of crude oil and natural gas from the United States.</p> <p>The President may provide an exemption to the requirement in specified circumstances.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
